content:
欢迎来到齿轮画廊！现在展出的有三个部分，请享受你在这里的时光。在[https://www.patreon.com/sunnyclockwork 这边]支持艺术家。

[[toc]]

@@@@
@@@@
------

+ 第一部分：收容项目

[[div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%"]]
[[html]]
<img id="pic" src="http://www.scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/2481%2001.jpg" width="150px" alt="" class="image" />
<script type="text/javascript">
var firstUrl = "https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/2481%2001.jpg";
var secondUrl = "http://www.scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/2481%2002.jpg";

new Image().src = firstUrl;

new Image().src = secondUrl;

window.onload = function(){

var org = window.document.getElementById('pic');
org.src = firstUrl;
org.onmouseover = function(ev){
this.src = secondUrl;
}
org.onmouseout = function(ev){
this.src = firstUrl;
}

 org.addEventListener('touchstart',org.onmouseover,false);
 org.addEventListener('touchend',org.onmouseout,false); 
}
</script>
[[/html]]

[[/div]]

[[div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%"]]

